```

### Key decisions
- System message is captured and merged into the first user turn (Mistral v0.3 convention)
- BOS token prepended via `tmpl.bos_token()` to produce `<s>[INST] ...`
- `COMMON_CHAT_FORMAT_CONTENT_ONLY` — no PEG parser, grammar, or tool-call handling needed
- `[SYSTEM_PROMPT]` absence in the detection condition safely distinguishes this from the existing Ministral-3 handler
- Message iteration follows the exact `msg.value("role", "")` / `msg.value("content", "")` pattern used everywhere else
